>
  <div class="x-one-brand-endorsement">
    <img
      class="pc lazyload x-one-brand-endorsement-img"
      data-src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0601/7820/2737/files/Why_Choose_Procolored.jpg?v=1770976983"
      alt=""
    >
    <img
      class="mb lazyload x-one-brand-endorsement-img"
      data-src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0509/3454/6613/files/Frame_2121235832.jpg?v=1772173030"
      alt=""
    >
    <div class="x-one-brand-endorsement-content">
      <div class="x-one-brand-endorsement-content-title">Why Choose Procolored!</div>
      <div class="x-one-brand-endorsement-content-desc">
        <div class="x-one-brand-endorsement-content-desc-text">
          <span>With deep-rooted expertise since 2018</span>
          , Procolored drives the future of customization with industry-leading DTF, UV, and UV-DTF solutions. We have
          spent years mastering UV printing technology to empower creators to transform fabric, acrylic, wood, metal,
          and ceramics into vibrant, professional-grade prints.
        </div>
        <div class="x-one-brand-endorsement-content-desc-text">
          Certified with the <span>G7 Master Facility Qualification</span>, the
          <span>Gold Standard for global color precision</span>, we guarantee that what you see on screen is exactly
          what you get in production, ensuring unrivaled quality in every project.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="x-one-brand-endorsement-content2">
      <div class="x-one-brand-endorsement-content2-img pc">
        <img
          class="lazyload "
          data-src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0509/3454/6613/files/Frame_2121235844.jpg?v=1772172943"
          alt=""
        >
      </div>
      <div class="x-one-brand-endorsement-content2-img mb">
