          class="lazyload"
          data-src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0509/3454/6613/files/Frame_2121235845.jpg?v=1772173030"
          alt=""
        >
      </div>
      <div class="x-one-brand-endorsement-content2-content-box">
        <div class="x-one-brand-endorsement-content2-title">
          <div class="x-one-brand-endorsement-content2-title-icon">
            <img
              class="lazyload "
              data-src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0509/3454/6613/files/Frame_54922.png?v=1772163634"
              alt=""
            >
          </div>
          <div class="x-one-brand-endorsement-content2-title-text">
            <div class="x-one-brand-endorsement-content2-title-text-logo">Global No.1</div>
            <div class="x-one-brand-endorsement-content2-title-text-tips">Desktop Direct-to-Object Printer</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="x-one-brand-endorsement-content2-desc">
          Recognized as a leading brand in the desktop Direct-to-Object Printer, our growth is powered by the trust of
          <span>150,000+</span> users worldwide. Customers choose Procolored for printers that are built to last and
          easy to use. By bringing industrial-grade precision into a desktop format, we empower creators to produce
          high-quality custom products — without the complexity of industrial systems.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="x-one-brand-endorsement-content3">
      <div class="x-one-brand-endorsement-content3-img pc">
        <img
          class="lazyload "
          data-src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0509/3454/6613/files/323123123123.jpg?v=1772172948"
          alt=""
        >
      </div>
      <div class="x-one-brand-endorsement-content3-img mb">
        <img
          class="lazyload"
          data-src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0509/3454/6613/files/Frame_212123584555.jpg?v=1772173030"
          alt=""
        >
      </div>
      <div class="x-one-brand-endorsement-content3-content-box">
        <div class="x-one-brand-endorsement-content3-title">
          <div class="x-one-brand-endorsement-content3-title-text">
            <div class="x-one-brand-endorsement-content3-title-text-logo">$1,800,000</div>
            <div class="x-one-brand-endorsement-content3-title-text-tips">
              <div class="x-one-brand-endorsement-content3-title-text-tips-text">729 Backers</div>
              <div class="x-one-brand-endorsement-content3-title-text-tips-img">
                <img
                  class="lazyload "
                  data-src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0509/3454/6613/files/Kickstarter-Logo_1_9c13bb4a-b7ab-4abc-9df2-8b7f344c5827.png?v=1772164814"
                  alt=""
                >
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="x-one-brand-endorsement-content3-desc">
          Procolored's previous generation — the K Series DTF printer — was a standout success on Kickstarter,
          <span>raising nearly $1.8M </span>and <span>attracting hundreds of backers.</span> This milestone not only
          validated Procolored’s product design and user experience but also helped build global momentum for our next
          generation of production-grade systems.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
